      MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification.ForMatchedMethod.onSuperCall()

      MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification.ForMatchedMethod.onVirtualCall()

      MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification MemberSubstitution.WithoutSpecification.ForMatchedField.onWrite()
